data.description: This is the renovation you have been looking for, hurry in!  Everything in this home is designer style and latest trends.  Craftsman style exterior painted brick and professionally landscaped.  Welcoming open concept living, dining, kitchen area with quartz counter tops, tile backsplash and stainless steel appliances. Original refinished hardwood floors throughout the home, lots of natural light in all rooms.  The Primary Suite is facing the quiet private back yard, huge walk-in closet, double vanity in the bathroom and a glass shower. This home has all new electrical, HVAC, roof, and plumbing.
